@DATABASE "Ghouls 'N' Ghosts 48K"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - Ghouls 'N' Ghosts 48K"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                           Ghouls 'N' Ghosts 48K
                           =====================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35612,128)"}          35612,x (x= 1-128)
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(35390,0)"}          35390,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
